# LaTeX modelagem always up to date

When changing pipeline behavior (Python tools, Nexus, DataShield, Optimus,
Critic, validator, config/thresholds, prompts, or contracts):

1. Update `docs/sense_to_respond_modelagem.tex` in the **same session**.
2. Recompile: `pdflatex docs/sense_to_respond_modelagem.tex` (twice if refs).
3. Document only what the code implements; planned features go under
   "Proximos Passos" (or equivalent), never as invariants.
4. Do not mark `docs/planning.md` items `[x]` while the LaTeX is stale.
5. Keep `.tex` ASCII with LaTeX escapes (`\'e`, `\c{c}`, etc.).

See also `rules.md` section 2.1.
